Text: You are receiving this text because you are listed as a customer of Cherry Hill Triplex. You may reply normally, or reply STOP to unsubscribe.

Hi STEPHEN!  This is Cherry Hill Triplex's Service Scheduling Department. Thank you for your online request for an appointment for your vehicle on 8/4. PLEASE NOTE: We do require all vehicles in need of a diagnostic appointment to be dropped off and left with us for the appointment. Drop off options are as follows:
The evening before, you may drop off with our cashier up until end of business that day. 
The morning of, you may drop off when we open at 8am. 
Please confirm by responding 'YES' and please indicate if you will be dropping and leaving your vehicle off the evening before or the morning of your appointment. Please feel free to call our scheduling department at 856-471-1058. Have a great day:)
Thank you so much for getting back to me. Will you be dropping off the night before or the morning of your appt?
Ok! Perfect. We will see you the morning of  8/4 for drop off. Have a great rest of your day!!
